VARDESC: Have you had a vaccination against COVID-19?
How many vaccines have you had?
COMMENT1: ASK IF \Have you had a vaccination against COVID-19?\" = \"Yes\""

VARDESC: Which vaccine did you have? (if more than 1: please answer in relation to your first vaccine)
COMMENT1: ASK IF \Have you had a vaccination against COVID-19?\" = \"Yes\""

VARDESC: When did you have the vaccine? (if more than 1: please answer in relation to your first vaccine)
COMMENT1: ASK IF \Have you had a vaccination against COVID-19?\" = \"Yes\""
ASK IF \How many vaccines have you had?\" = \"2\" or \"How many vaccines have you had?\" = \"3\""

VARDESC: When did you have the second vaccine?
COMMENT1: ASK IF \How many vaccines have you had?\" = \"2\" or \"How many vaccines have you had?\" = \"3\""
ASK IF \How many vaccines have you had?\" = \"3\""

VARDESC: When did you have the third vaccine?
COMMENT1: ASK IF \How many vaccines have you had?\" = \"3\""
